OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy start with a mixture of
OL,6,Fsunny spells and showers, occasionally
OL,7,Fheavy. Winds will ease through the
OL,8,Fday, with showers also fading into the
OL,9,Fevening. Temperatures cooler than on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry with some evening
OL,13,Fsunshine in the northeast, cloud
OL,14,Fthickening from the southwest,
OL,15,Fbringing late-evening rain, heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes. Winds strengthen later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
