OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FBreezy. Rain initially light,
OL,6,Fturning heavier mid-morning before
OL,7,Fclearing east. Isolated afternoon
OL,8,Fshowers possible, with brighter or
OL,9,Fsunny spells developing by evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells and showers Saturday. Drier and
OL,13,Fsunnier with winds easing Sunday.
OL,14,FCloudier on Monday with showers
OL,15,Fspreading inland from coastal areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
